    "By tackling these challenges, the proposed method aims to not only enhance GPT-Neo's applicability and relevance but also pave the way for future innovations in the field of generative AI.",
    "This paper will detail the conceptual framework, implementation strategies, and evaluation metrics for incremental knowledge enrichment, setting the stage for a new era of dynamic and self-updating language models.",
    "This study makes the following contributions:1.",
    "Introduced a novel approach for Incremental Knowledge Enrichment in GPT-Neo, enabling the model to integrate and utilize real-time information without the need for full retraining. 2.",
    "Developed and integrated a Dynamic Linking Mechanism within GPT-Neo, facilitating seamless access to and incorporation of data from diverse external sources, enhancing the model's accuracy, timeliness, and relevance."
